    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    Applicant
    Represents an applicant in the BTO Management System.
    ApplicantUI
    UI class for Applicant users with filtering capabilities
    Application
    Represents a BTO housing application submitted by an applicant.
    ApplicationRepository
    Constructs a new Application Repository instance.
    ApplicationStatus
    Represents the possible statuses of a BTO application.
    BaseUserUI
    Base class for all user interface classes Contains common functionality shared by all user types
    Enquiry
    Represents an enquiry submitted by an applicant regarding a BTO project.
    EnquiryRepository
    Constructs a new Enquiry Repository instance.
    EnquiryStatus
    Represents the possible statuses of an enquiry in the BTO system.
    FileHandler
    Utility class for handling file operations in the BTO system.
    FlatType
    Represents the types of flats available in BTO projects.
    HdbManager
    Represents an HDB Manager in the BTO Management System.
    HdbOfficer
    Represents an HDB Officer in the BTO Management System.
    IApplicationProcessing
    Defines operations for processing BTO applications.
    IEnquiryManagement
    Defines operations for managing enquiries in the BTO system.
    IProjectManagement
    Defines operations for managing BTO projects.
    IRepository<T>
    Generic repository interface that defines standard operations for data access across different entity types.
    MainUI
    Main entry point for the BTO Management System.
    ManagerUI
    UI class for HDB Manager users in the BTO system.
    MaritalStatus
    Represents the marital status of a user in the BTO system.
    OfficerRegistrationStatus
    Represents the status of an HDB Officer's registration to handle a project.
    OfficerUI
    UI class for HDB Officer users in the BTO system.
    Project
    Represents a Build-To-Order (BTO) housing project.
    ProjectFilter
    Utility class to filter and sort projects based on user preferences.
    ProjectRepository
    Constructs a new Project Repository instance.
    Receipt
    Represents a receipt for a successful flat booking in the BTO system.
    Report
    Represents a report generated in the BTO system.
    ReportType
    Represents the types of reports that can be generated in the BTO system.
    User
    Represents a user in the BTO Management System.
    UserRepository
    Constructs a new User Repository instance.
